red riding hood is a 2011 canadian romance horror film directed by catherine hardwicke , produced by leonardo dicaprio and starring amanda seyfried as the title role , from a screenplay by david leslie johnson . the film is very loosely based on the folk tale little red riding hood collected by both charles perrault under the name le petit &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; rouge ( little red riding hood ) and several decades later by the brothers grimm as &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( little red cap ) . despite negative reviews , the movie was commercially successful grossing almost $ 90 millions worldwide .